---
title: Crumbed Tofu Dippers & Fries with Charred Corn Salad & Chipotle Mayo
description: Crumbed to golden perfection, these crispy tofu bites are a dippin' delight! We've teamed them with a chipotle mayo to dive into, plus a fresh salad with sweet charred corn kernels and baked potato fries.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ddf414cf3e6147286036a88-35afcb1c.jpg
